<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Edward" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Edward,</orth> 1) E. Confessor: <bibl n="shak. h8 4.1.88" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 IV, 1, 88</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 3.6.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 6, 27</bibl>. 2) E. the Third: <bibl n="shak. r2 1.2.11" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 2, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.1.121" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 121</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.4.128" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 4, 128</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 1.1.89" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 I, 1, 89</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 1.2.248" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 248</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.2.31" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 2, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.4.84" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 84</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.5.66" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 5, 66</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.2.10" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 2, 10</bibl>. -- 3) E. the Black Prince: <bibl n="shak. h5 1.2.105" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 I, 2, 105</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.4.56" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 56</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.7.97" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 7, 97</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.5.64" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 5, 64</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.2.11" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 2, 11</bibl>. -- 4) E. Prince of Wales, son of Henry VI: <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.1.259" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 1, 259</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.60" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 60</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.31" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 31</bibl> etc. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.10" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 10</bibl> etc. -- 5) E. the Fourth: <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.2.40" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 2, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.4.11" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 4, 11</bibl>. 74 etc. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.1.36" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 1, 36</bibl> etc. -- 6) E. the Fifth: <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.199" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 199</bibl> etc. -- 7) E. the Sixth: <cit><quote>two E. shovel-boards,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.159" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 159</bibl></cit>; cf. <emph>Shovel-board.</emph> -- 8) E. duke of York: <bibl n="shak. h5 4.8.108" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 8, 108</bibl>. -- 9) E. duke of Bar: <bibl n="shak. h5 4.8.103" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 8, 103</bibl>. -- 10) Sir E. Courtney: <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.502" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 4, 502</bibl> (Qq <emph>William</emph>). -- 11) E. Bohun (duke of Buckingham): <bibl n="shak. h8 2.1.103" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 1, 103</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>